    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Kiriko teleports to her tank via Swift Step to keep pace with a dive, cleansing crowd control with Protection Suzu and healing through Ofuda while looking for an opening to finish a weakened enemy with Kunai.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Wall Climb and Swift Step both put her in exposed positions between cooldowns, and she has no barrier, so sustained hitscan pressure can burn her down quickly.</p>\n"
